In addition, for James Gregory (1638-1675), the Elder, the UK National
		  Register of Archives (NRA), updated by the Historical Manuscripts Commission,
		  notes these other collections: papers, British Library, Manuscript Collections,
		  Ref. Sloane MS 3208; correspondence with John Collins, 1667-1675, Private;
		  correspondence with John Collins, 1668-1675, St. Andrews University Library;
		  and, correspondence with John Collins etc, 1669-1674, Royal Society.
